01:29:43.530 --> 01:29:48.010
if you've already bought them. So we're going
to be there for just about an hour. We have

01:29:48.010 --> 01:29:54.450
to be out of the building at 9:30. So that
is our deadline. So head out the front and

01:29:54.450 --> 01:29:58.080
you'll see Billy there. Thanks very much once
again on the behalf of the American Folklife

01:29:58.080 --> 01:29:59.460
Center and the Library of Congress.

